steps.name: Given  the user logs in with username "Employee140" and password "Employee123"
And  user navigates to File page
When  user choose Details on the file "Salam World"
And  user click on Comment button
And  user ads comment "Please follow me on istagram"
Then  user should see comment "Please follow me on istagram" under the comment section
